Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:59.19,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,350)}Even so, I walked on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:04.82,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(230,400)}That's what it was to be strong
