Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:40.02,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}They'll continue to live only through their memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:47.82,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Rather than try to love and laugh at this loneliness
