Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.00,0:24:19.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c44] The band is dying because of your guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:19.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c164] Tenshi... you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.65,0:24:20.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c47] As I thought, not one to be taken lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.42,0:24:21.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c47] I know that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:23.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c141] German Suplex!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:22.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c75] It's just something I wanted to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:22.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c192] Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:23.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c162] Has your idiocy been cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.54,0:24:24.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c185] We men will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.11,0:24:25.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c210] Hey, which side are you on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.63,0:24:24.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c173] KISS YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:25.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c218] It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.25,0:24:26.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c105] Alright! I'll grant it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.61,0:24:28.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c289] All of my happiness was taken away...
